.TH mps 1  "mps 0.8.11" 
.SH NAME
mps \- Start the moshpits server
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmps\fR [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR]... [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR]... [\fB\-e\fR|\fB\-\-enable\-std\-output\fR] [\fB\-c\fR|\fB\-\-config\-absolute\-path\fR] [\fB\-t\fR|\fB\-\-tracing\-absolute\-path\fR] [\fB\-p\fR|\fB\-\-private\-key\-path\fR] [\fB\-k\fR|\fB\-\-public\-key\-path\fR] [\fB\-\-warmup\-delay\-ms\fR] [\fB\-\-pacing\-delay\-us\fR] [\fB\-\-term\-type\fR] [\fB\-\-kex\-algos\fR] [\fB\-\-aead\-algos\fR] [\fB\-\-mac\-algos\fR] [\fB\-\-kdf\-algos\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Start the moshpits server
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Turn up logging verbosity (multiple will turn it up more)
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Turn down logging verbosity (multiple will turn it down more)
.TP
\fB\-e\fR, \fB\-\-enable\-std\-output\fR
Enable logging to stdout/stderr
.TP
\fB\-c\fR, \fB\-\-config\-absolute\-path\fR \fI<PATH>\fR
Specify the absolute path to the config file
.TP
\fB\-t\fR, \fB\-\-tracing\-absolute\-path\fR \fI<PATH>\fR
Specify the absolute path to the tracing output file
.TP
\fB\-p\fR, \fB\-\-private\-key\-path\fR \fI<PATH>\fR
Specify the absolute path to the private key file
.TP
\fB\-k\fR, \fB\-\-public\-key\-path\fR \fI<PATH>\fR
Specify the absolute path to the public key file
.TP
\fB\-\-warmup\-delay\-ms\fR \fI<MILLIS>\fR
Extra delay (ms) after peer discovery before sending terminal data
.TP
\fB\-\-pacing\-delay\-us\fR \fI<MICROS>\fR [default: 1000]
Min inter\-packet delay (µs) between diff chunks [default: 1000]
.TP
\fB\-\-term\-type\fR \fI<TERM>\fR [default: xterm\-256color]
TERM environment variable for spawned shells (default: xterm\-256color)
.TP
\fB\-\-kex\-algos\fR \fI<ALGOS>\fR
Ordered KEX algorithms to prefer, comma\-separated [supported: x25519\-sha256 (default), ml\-kem\-768\-sha256, ml\-kem\-512\-sha256, ml\-kem\-1024\-sha256, p384\-sha384, p256\-sha256]
.TP
\fB\-\-aead\-algos\fR \fI<ALGOS>\fR
Ordered AEAD algorithms to prefer, comma\-separated [supported: aes256\-gcm\-siv (default), aes256\-gcm, chacha20\-poly1305, aes128\-gcm\-siv]
.TP
\fB\-\-mac\-algos\fR \fI<ALGOS>\fR
Ordered MAC algorithms to prefer, comma\-separated [supported: hmac\-sha512 (default), hmac\-sha256]
.TP
\fB\-\-kdf\-algos\fR \fI<ALGOS>\fR
Ordered KDF algorithms to prefer, comma\-separated [supported: hkdf\-sha256 (default), hkdf\-sha384, hkdf\-sha512]
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH VERSION
v0.8.11
